<localDeveloperName>Loan_Status_Inquiry</localDeveloperName>
<masterLabel>Loan Status Inquiry</masterLabel>
<pluginType>Topic</pluginType>
<scope>Use this action when a user requests to check or retrieve the status of their loan application.

This action supports both authenticated and unauthenticated users:

For authenticated users, it uses available session context (such as ContactId or AccountId) to identify the customer.

For unauthenticated users, it requests the customer’s registered email address to locate their loan application.

The action retrieves all loan applications associated with the identified customer. If multiple applications are found, it presents the list and allows the user to select one. If a single application is found, it returns the status directly.

This action is not intended for creating, modifying, or submitting loan applications. It is strictly used for retrieving and viewing the status of existing loan applications.</scope>
